replies.body:
[Why are you ignoring Cassiopeia's plight entirely after all the recent threads?](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/gameplay-balance/rBbcJyIV-cassiopeia-a-history-of-ongoing-neglection) {{champion:69}}

How can you even have immobile mages on your buff list while omitting the snakelady at the same time? She's among the weakest midlaners in the game right now, that's statistically proven. **Not even her small dedicated playerbase can make her work anymore.** She's in an extremely questionable state and needs YOUR help,  yet none of your red buddies want to talk about her.

[Why are you deliberately avoiding topics like this one?](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/gameplay-balance/pqmfvPyR-riot-meddler-ive-got-one-simple-question-for-you)
